2006;;Civic Duty;;American;;Jeff Renfroe;;Peter Krause, Khaled Abol Naga, Richard Schiff;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Civic_Duty_(film);;The film is about an American accountant bombarded with cable news and the media's obsession with terrorist plots in the post 9/11 world, who receives a jolt when an unattached Islamic graduate student moves in next door.